{"tid":2164464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁頌恆拖欠立法會93萬   遭入稟呈請破產","createTime":"2020-08-19T08:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T08:35:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7498d0545c6c49785f8e14a0161e143cbda8d682","tid":2164464,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2020/08/19/xujiachun_cbc9836883bbb458b86543c3177a8c2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2020%2F08%2F19%2Fxujiachun_cbc9836883bbb458b86543c3177a8c2d.png&h=7fd4ca45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【文匯網訊】大公文匯全媒體報道：因宣揚「港獨」、侮辱國家和民族，被DQ的前立法會議員游蕙禎、梁頌恆，早前被立法會入稟追討已發放的酬金、利息及訟費，游蕙禎提出分期還款獲接納，但梁頌恆就未有理會。立法會行政管理委員會昨日（18日）入稟高院呈請要梁頌恆破產。司法機構已排期在今年12月2日開庭審訊這宗呈請。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆因拖欠立法會93萬港元的已放酬金、利息及訟費，早前已被行管會入稟追討欠款，惟梁頌恆未有理會，法院於是直接判處行管會勝訴，下令他須清還1個月立法會議員薪金9萬多港元，以及行管會分別預支給他們的83萬多港元。因梁未有按判令還款，行管會於上月開會後，決定呈請梁破產<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2020/08/19/IN2008190045.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F08%2F19%2FIN2008190045.htm&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=025f2ba4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2020/08/19/IN2008190045.htm</a>"},{"pid":"72ad629f9c84cb8a5d0b1b1fb842ecc2c6723a2d","tid":2164464,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"只係93萬, <br />\n<br />\n應唔應該眾籌幫一幫手？"},{"pid":"3388a11865a0f433f29e16dd87371428ae23858a","tid":2164464,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72ad629f9c84cb8a5d0b1b1fb842ecc2c6723a2d","tid":2164464,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"只係93萬, <br />\n<br />\n應唔應該眾籌幫一幫手？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"留錢去外國仲好啦"},{"pid":"b949d3e039bad36a5ac25ec180f74c29f485a92f","tid":2164464,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu